data.description: Supurb location close to I-30, 635, Hwy 80 and easy access to downtown Dallas! 3 oversized bedrooms, split master suite has private ensuite with large walk in closet. Open flowing floorplan! Kitchen with abudance of cabinets and counter space, open flex space currently used as home office could serve as formal dining! Attic features Radiant Barrier for energy conservation. Large private backyard with karge open patio and low maintenance vinyl fence. Enjoy the holidays with family and friends in your new home!
